text: Polyakovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Polyakovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 384 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Polyakovka
